xposed%20to%20corporate%20America.%20I%20didn't%20grow%20up%20around%20corporate%20functions%20or%20know%20what%20investment%20banking%20or%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fconsulting-firms-mckinsey-bcg-accenture-workers-leaving-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econsulting%20space%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20college%2C%20I%20learned%20more%20about%20consulting%20and%20saw%20it%20as%20a%20good%20field%20for%20someone%20like%20me%20who%20wanted%20to%20be%20a%20generalist%20and%20work%20on%20problem-solving.%20I%20took%20part%20in%20consulting%20extracurriculars%20and%20landed%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-get-summer-intership-mckinsey-management-consulting-2021-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einternship%20at%20McKinsey%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20summer%20of%20my%20third%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20internship%2C%20I%20joined%20McKinsey%20full-time%20as%20a%20business%20analyst%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20stayed%20at%20McKinsey%20for%20around%20two%20years%20and%20then%20left%20to%20take%20on%20a%20director%20of%20strategy%20and%20business%20operations%20role%20for%20a%20tech%20company.%20My%20tenure%20at%20McKinsey%20strengthened%20my%20ability%20to%20build%20relationships%20in%20professional%20environments%2C%20a%20skill%20that%20has%20helped%20me%20throughout%20my%20career.%20I've%20also%20been%20using%20a%20fun%20term%20to%20describe%20this%20skill%3A%20biz%20rizz.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220a62cec7-f1b0-4a6d-80d7-f815d1ee3bfe%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMentors%20helped%20me%20with%20relationship-building%20skills%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20started%20at%20McKinsey%2C%20I%20was%20linked%20up%20with%20a%20professional%20development%20manager%20who%20helped%20staff%20me%20on%20projects.%20In%20consulting%2C%20you%20don't%20really%20have%20a%20set%20manager%20and%20team%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20all%20project-based.%20Every%20few%20weeks%20or%20months%2C%20you're%20working%20with%20new%20people%2C%20clients%2C%20and%20often%20in%20new%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20obviously%20hard%20skills%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fconsulting-firms-sponsors-secret-to-success-mckinsey-accenture-consultants-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econsultants%20should%20have%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20like%20making%20Excel%20models%20and%20analysis%2C%20but%20also%20soft%20skills%20%E2%80%94%20the%20ability%20to%20build%20relationships%20with%20clients.%20Some%20of%20this%20was%20formally%20taught%2C%20such%20as%20in%20a%20training%20session%20about%20trust%2C%20but%20I%20also%20developed%20soft%20skills%20organically.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20my%20biggest%20barriers%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fways-to-build-strong-and-authentic-relationships-at-work-2021-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edeveloping%20relationships%20in%20the%20workplace%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20confidence%20and%20comfort.%20At%20McKinsey%2C%20you%20can%20be%2021%20sitting%20in%20a%20room%20with%20C-Suite%20executives%2C%20which%20can%20be%20intimidating.%20You%20overthink%20in%20those%20situations%20about%20what's%20appropriate%20to%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20my%20parents%20found%20out%20I%20had%20this%20job%2C%20they%20advised%20me%20to%20keep%20my%20head%20down%2C%20but%20I%20think%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-build-relationships-with-coworkers-from-home-2020-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprofessional%20relationship-building%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20important.%20I%20tried%20figuring%20out%20how%20to%20network%20and%20make%20small%20talk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20lucky%20to%20have%20great%20mentors%20on%20my%20first%20projects.%20One%20of%20my%20managers%20coached%20me%20to%20present%20to%20a%20C-suite%20executive.%20One%20of%20my%20mentors%20told%20me%20to%20think%20about%20the%20executive%20as%20my%20friend's%20uncle