%2C%20and%20was%20also%20a%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Munde's%20Parli%20seat%20was%20formed%20in%202009%20and%20won%20by%20his%20cousin%2C%20the%20BJP's%20Pankaja%20Munde%2C%20in%20the%20first%20two%20state%20elections.%20In%20the%202019%20and%202024%20polls%20it%20was%20Mr%20Munde%20who%20took%20over%3B%20first%20for%20the%20undivided%20NCP%20led%20by%20Sharad%20Pawar%20and%20then%20for%20the%20NCP%20faction%20led%20by%20Ajit%20Pawar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20previous%20government%2C%20led%20by%20Shiv%20Sena%20boss%20Eknath%20Shinde%2C%20Dhanjay%20Munde%20served%20as%20the%20Agriculture%20Minister%20from%20July%202023%20to%20November%202024%2C%20when%20the%20Assembly%20election%20was%20held.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20that%20time%20he%20was%20also%20the%20'guardian%20minister'%20for%20Beed%20district%2C%20a%20position%20that%20has%20since%20been%20given%20to%20party%20colleague%20Manikrao%20Kokate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Munde%20was%20also%20a%20cabinet%20member%20when%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%2C%20boss%20of%20the%20then-undivided%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20was%20Chief%20Minister%3B%20Mr%20Thackeray%20led%20an%20alliance%20of%20the%20Sena%2C%20the%20(then-also%20undivided)%20NCP%2C%20and%20the%20Congress.%20He%20was%20then%20Minister%20for%20Social%20Justice%20and%20Special%20Assistance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Munde%20has%20often%20faced%20controversial%20situations%20in%20a%20career%20spanning%20nearly%20two%20decades%2C%20including%20charges%20of%20rape%20in%20January%202021.%20These%20were%20made%20by%20a%20popular%20singer%20but%20later%20withdrawn.%20Mr%20Munde%20denied%20all%20allegations%20and%20stared%20down%20the%20opposition's%20calls%20to%20quit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20then%20a%20minister%20in%20Uddhav%20Thackeray's%20cabinet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EPolitical%20Career%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Munde%20began%20his%20career%20working%20with%20his%20uncle%2C%20Gopinath%20Munde%2C%20and%20helping%20manage%20the%20family's%20political%20interests%20in%20Beed.%20He%20also%20marked%20himself%20out%20as%20an%20excellent%20orator.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndeed%2C%20many%20even%20saw%20him%20as%20the%20senior%20BJP%20leader's%20'heir%20apparent'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20changed%20in%202009%2C%20after%20Gopinath%20Munde%20picked%20his%20daughter%2C%20Pankaja%2C%20to%20represent%20the%20family%20seat%20of%20Parli.%20Then%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20party%20offered%20him%20a%20position%20in%20the%20Legislative%20Council.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20relationship%20never%20really%20recovered%2C%20and%20in%202012%20he%20switched%20to%20the%20NCP%2C%20which%20was%20then%20led%20by%20Sharad%20Pawar.%20Mr%20Munde's%20father%2C%20Panditrao%20Munde%2C%20made%20the%20same%20jump%20months%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDhananjay%20Munde%20contested%20the%202014%20election%20against%20his%20cousin%20but%20lost.%20He%20regrouped%20and%20returned%20five%20years%20later%2C%20flipping%20a%20defeat%20by%2026%2C000%20votes%20into%20a%20victory%20by%20more%20than%2040%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202023%20he%20sided%20with%20Ajit%20Pawar%20in%20his%20rebellion%20against%20his%20uncle%20and%20NCP%20founder%20Sharad%20Pawar.%20The%20younger%20Pawar%20was%20reportedly%20keen%20on%20signing%20Mr%20Munde%20on%20to%20diversify%20his%20NCP%20faction's%20identity%20as%20more%20than%20a%20Maratha-centric%20political%20outfit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20return%2C%20Mr%20Munde%20has%20been%20seen%20as%20an%20Ajit%20Pawar%20loyalist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Sarpanch%20Murder%20Fallout%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWalmik%20Karad%2C%20the%20prime%20accused%20in%20the%20torture%20and%20murder%20of%20the%20sarpanch%20Santosh%20Deshmukh%2C%20is%20a%20confidante%20of%20Mr%20Munde%2C%20and%20it%20was%20that%20closeness%20that%20gave%20the%20opposition%20enough%20ammunition%20to%20press%20for%20the%20NCP%20leader's%20sacking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdhananjay-munde-santosh-deshmukh-walmik-karad-behind-maharashtra-ministers-ouster-a-sarpanchs-torture-and-murder-7844287%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECrime%2C%20Clout%2C%20Caste%3A%20In-Between%20Sarpanch%20Murder%20And%20Minister's%20Exit%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20that%20after%20details%20of%20the%20police%20case%20were%20made%20public%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20met%20Ajit%20Pawar%20to%20discuss%20the%20potential%20fallout%20of%20that%20link%20and%2C%20eventually%2C%20Mr%20Munde%20was%20asked%20to%20quit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fready-to-resign-if-maharashtra-minister-dhananjay-munde-on-resignation-calls-amid-beed-sarpanch-murder-case-7587953%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BReady%20If...%26quot%3B%3A%20Dhananjay%20Munde%20On%20Quit%20Calls%20Amid%20Murder%20Case%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20controversy%20over%20the%20sarpanch's%20murder%20grew%2C%20in%20January%20Mr%20Munde%20said%20he%20would%20have%20no%20problem%20resigning%20if%20asked%20to%2C%20either%20by%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20or%20Mr%20Pawar.%20%26quot%3BIf%20Chief%20Minister%20Fadnavis%20or%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Pawar%20believe%20I%20am%20guilty...%20they%20should%20ask%20for%20my%20resignation.%20I%20am%20ready%20to%20step%20down.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Fchannel%2F0029Va4lixw7z4kcvZI9JM12%5C%22%3EClick%20on%20the%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20all%20the%20latest%20updates%20from%20NDTV%20on%20your%20chat.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741080180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Ffajspavo_dhananjay-munde_650x400_04_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbeed-sarpanch-santosh-deshmukh-murde