20of%20local%20residents.%20Determined%20to%20stop%20this%2C%20he%20took%20on%20Ghule.%20On%20December%206%2C%20three%20days%20before%20the%20murder%2C%20Ghule%20and%20others%20beat%20up%20some%20Avaada%20employees%20at%20its%20local%20office.%20Santosh%20Deshmukh%20and%20others%20reached%20the%20spot%20and%20tried%20to%20stop%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20police%2C%20the%20accused%20felt%20Santosh%20Deshmukh%20was%20coming%20in%20the%20way%20of%20their%20plans%20and%20decided%20to%20eliminate%20him.%20Walmik%20Karad%2C%20named%20the%20mastermind%20in%20the%20murder%20case%2C%20allegedly%20asked%20the%20other%20accused%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20whoever%20came%20in%20the%20way%20of%20the%20extortion%20bid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeshmukh%20was%20threatened%20several%20times.%20When%20he%20did%20not%20fall%20in%20line%2C%20he%20was%20abducted%20and%20killed%20on%20December%209.%20Police%20found%20that%20Ghule%2C%20Karad%20and%20Vishnu%20Chate%20were%20in%20touch%20with%20each%20other%20before%20and%20after%20Deshmukh's%20murder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Images%20of%20a%20tortured%20Santosh%20Deshmukh%20in%20the%20police%20chargesheet%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Images%20of%20a%20tortured%20Santosh%20Deshmukh%20in%20the%20police%20chargesheet%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F3fvg6s3g_chargesheet_625x300_04_March_25.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImages%20of%20a%20tortured%20Santosh%20Deshmukh%20in%20the%20police%20chargesheet%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBrutal%20Torture%2C%20Shocking%20Videos%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESantosh%20Deshmukh%20was%20abducted%20by%20six%20men%20in%20an%20SUV%20on%20December%209%20afternoon%20at%20Dongaon%20toll%20plaza%20and%20taken%20towards%20Kej%20taluka.%20He%20was%20found%20unconscious%20at%20Daithna%20Shivar%20that%20evening.%20He%20was%20rushed%20to%20a%20hospital%2C%20where%20he%20was%20declared%20dead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20police%20officials%2C%20he%20was%20beaten%20for%20over%20two%20hours%20with%20a%20gas%20pipe%20an%20iron%20rod%2C%20wooden%20sticks%20and%20sharp%20weapons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20have%20said%20in%20the%20chargesheet%20that%20Santosh%20Deshmukh%20was%20tortured%20before%20being%20killed%20and%20the%20assailants%20recorded%2015%20videos%2C%20clicked%20eight%20photos%20and%20even%20made%20two%20video%20calls%20to%20document%20the%20brutality.%20In%20one%20of%20the%20videos%20mentioned%20in%20the%20chargesheet%2C%20five%20accused%20are%20seen%20thrashing%20Mr%20Deshmukh%20with%20a%20white%20pipe%20and%20a%20wooden%20stick%2C%20and%20kicking%20and%20punching%20him.%20The%20video%20shows%20Deshmukh%20in%20a%20half-naked%20condition.%20Another%20video%20shows%20one%20of%20the%20accused%20urinating%20on%20him%20as%20he%20bleeds%20heavily%2C%20the%20chargesheet%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Flames%20Scalded%20Minister%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWalmik%20Karad%2C%20the%20prime%20accused%20in%20the%20chilling%20murder%20case%2C%20is%20a%20close%20aide%20of%20NCP%20leader%20and%20then%20minister%20Dhananjay%20Munde.%20As%20Karad's%20alleged%20role%20in%20the%20shocking%20murder%20emerged%20during%20the%20probe%2C%20the%20Opposition%20started%20demanding%20action.%20The%20Crime%20Investigation%20Department's%20(CID)%201%2C200-page%20chargesheet%20provided%20more%20ammo%20to%20the%20Opposition.%20As%20chilling%20visuals%20documenting%20the%20brutality%20suffered%20by%20Deshmukh%20flashed%20on%20social%20media%20and%20TV%20screens%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20took%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20sources%2C%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20met%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20NCP%20chief%20Ajit%20Pawar%20to%20discuss%20the%20political%20fallout%20of%20the%20chargesheet%20and%20what%20the%20investigation%20revealed%20about%20Karad's%20alleged%20role.%20Eventually%2C%20he%