usk's%20history%20of%20ruthlessly%20slimming%20down%20his%20companies%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20making%20them%20wildly%20successful%20give%20him%20the%20experience%20he%20needs%20to%20sniff%20out%20and%20cut%20Washington%20waste%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20predicted%20that%20Musk%20would%20have%20less%20unilateral%20power%20to%20enact%20his%20will%20than%20he%20does%20in%20the%20headquarters%20of%20X%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-salary-database-elon-musk-pay-strategy-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ETesla%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20federal%20government%20is%20not%20ruled%20by%20a%20king%2C%20after%20all%2C%20let%20alone%20an%20unelected%20%26quot%3Bspecial%20government%20employee.%26quot%3B%20But%20they%20didn't%20doubt%20Musk%2C%20given%20that%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftwitter-x-elon-musk-startup-competitition-town-square-election-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Egutted%20Twitter's%20staff%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%E2%80%94%20defying%20expectations%20that%20the%20platform%20would%20break%20%E2%80%94%20somehow%20kept%20it%20alive.%20As%20the%20Columbia%20Business%20School%20professor%20Michael%20Morris%20told%20me%2C%20sometimes%20it%20takes%20%26quot%3Bcreative%20destruction%26quot%3B%20to%20make%20radical%20changes%20to%20large%20organizations.%20On%20the%20whole%2C%20the%20experts%20were%20cautiously%20hopeful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20the%20fall%2C%20when%20all%20anyone%20could%20do%20was%20speculate.%20Today%2C%20six%20weeks%20into%20DOGE's%20existence%2C%20we%20have%20a%20%3Cem%3Elot%20%3C%2Fem%3Eof%20data.%20DOGE%20has%20created%20a%20dizzying%20tornado%20of%20news.%20Musk%20has%20used%20it%20to%20test%20the%20limits%20of%20the%20law%2C%20such%20as%20by%20dismantling%20USAID%2C%20a%20move%20that%20many%20legal%20experts%20have%20called%20unconstitutional.%20Tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20federal%20workers%20have%20been%20hastily%