sembly%20clean%20is%20our%20responsibility...If%20the%20MLA%20in%20question%20comes%20and%20tells%20me%20that%20they%20have%20done%20this%2C%20it%20will%20be%20good%3B%20otherwise%2C%20I%20will%20call%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Finance%20Minister%20Suresh%20Kumar%20Khanna%20on%20February%2020%20presented%20state%20budget%20for%20the%20year%202025-26.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20asserted%20that%20the%20state's%20budget%20is%209.8%20per%20cent%20higher%20than%20the%202024-25%20budget%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20infrastructure%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20press%20conference%2C%20CM%20Yogi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20budget%20is%20over%208%2C08%2C736%20crore%20Rs%2C%20which%20is%209.8%20per%20cent%20higher%20than%20the%202024-25%20budget.%20On%20one%20hand%2C%20the%20growth%20in%20the%20budget%20size%20reflects%20the%20state's%20strength%2C%20while%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20it%20also%20shows%20the%20commitment%20of%20the%20double-engine%20government.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20highlighted%20that%20while%20UP's%20economy%20was%20previously%20ranked%206th-7th%20in%20the%20country%2C%20it%20is%20now%20the%20second-largest%20economy%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAccording%20to%20the%20report%20by%20NITI%20Aayog%20on%20the%20fiscal%20health%20of%20states%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20has%20been%20placed%20in%20the%20front-runner%20category.%20Between%202018%20and%202022%2C%20the%20state's%20physical%20health%20index%20increased%20by%208.9%20per%20cent%2C%20and%20during%20this%20period%2C%20UP%20succeeded%20in%20reducing%20unemployment%20and%20creating%20additional%20jobs%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20highlighted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B22%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20total%20budget%20has%20been%20allocated%20to%20infrastructure%20development.%20For%20education%2C%201%2C06%2C360%20crore%20Rs%20has%20been%20allocated%2C%20which%20is%2013%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20total%20budget.%20While%20there%20is%20usually%20a%206%20per%20cent%20demand%20for%20education%2C%20UP%20is%20one%20of%20the%20states%20in%20the%20country%20that%20spends%2013%20per%20cent%20of%20its%20budget%20on%20education%2C%26quot%3B%20CM%20Yogi%20emphasized.%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20CM%20also%20outlined%20that%2011%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20total%20budget%20has%20been%20proposed%20for%20agriculture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20healthcare%2C%20the%20government%20has%20allocated%2050%20thousand%20550%20crore%20Rs%2C%20which%20is%206%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20total%20budget.%20For%20the%20Social%20Welfare%20Department%2C%20a%20provision%20of%2035%20thousand%20863%20crore%20Rs%20has%20been%20made%2C%20which%20will%20be%20used%20for%20the%20welfare%20of%20Scheduled%20Castes%2C%20Scheduled%20Tribes%2C%20backward%20classes%2C%20persons%20with%20disabilities%2C%20women%2C%20and%20child%20development%2C%26quot%3B%20CM%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741076160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F25d9dba_up-speaker_625x300_04_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fup-speaker-slams-mla-for-spitting-pan-masala-in-assembly-ive-seen-him-7844452%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Uttar%20Pradesh%20Assembly%20Speaker%20Satish%20Mahana%20revealed%20that%20he%20personally%20cleaned%20the%20area%20after%20receiving%20information%20about%20the%20incident.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fup-speaker-slams-mla-for-spitting-pan-masala-in-assembly-ive-seen-him-7844452%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Will%20fight%20them%20to%20bitter%20end'%3A%20China