emi-final-clash%2Farticleshow%2F118703346.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BStates%20Have%20Failed...%26quot%3B%3A%20Supreme%20Court%20On%20Affordable%20Drugs%2C%20Medical%20Equipment%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EState%20governments%20have%20failed%20in%20ensuring%20affordable%20medical%20care%20and%20infrastructure%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fsupreme-court%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESupreme%20Court%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20Tuesday%2C%20offering%20scathing%20criticism%20of%20states'%20failure%20to%20deliver%20reasonably-priced%20medicines%2C%20particularly%20in%20case%20of%20essential%20drugs%2C%20for%20people%20from%20poorer%20sections%20of%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20failure%2C%20the%20court%20noted%20had%20%26quot%3Bfacilitated%20and%20promoted%20private%20hospitals%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20of%20Justice%20Surya%20Kant%20and%20NK%20Singh%20was%20hearing%20a%20Public%20Interest%20Litigation%20arguing%20that%20private%20hospitals%20were%20compelling%20patients%2C%20and%20their%20families%2C%20to%20buy%20medicines%2C%20implants%2C%20and%20other%20medical%20care%20items%20from%20in-house%20pharmacies%20that%20imposed%20exorbitant%20mark-ups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PIL%20sought%20direction%20to%20private%20hospitals%20to%20not%20compel%20the%20patients%20to%20purchase%20only%20from%20the%20hospital%20pharmacies%20and%20alleged%20also%20that%20the%20centre%20and%20states%20had%20failed%20to%20take%20regulatory%20and%20correctional%20measures%2C%20as%20a%20result%20of%20which%20patients%20are%20being%20exploited.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20agree%20with%20you...%20but%20how%20to%20regulate%20this%3F%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Surya%20Kant%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20eventually%20noted%20it%20is%20the%20duty%20of%20states%20to%20ensure%20proper%20medical%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20observed%20also%20that%20some%20states%20had%20not%20been%20able%20to%20deliver%20the%20requisite%20medical%20care%20and%2C%20therefore%2C%20had%20%26quot%3Bfacilitated%20and%20promoted%20private%20entities%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20state%20governments%20were%20told%20to%20regulate%20such%20entities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20were%20told%20to%20ensure%20private%20hospitals%20do%20not%20compel%20patients%2C%20and%20families%2C%20to%20buy%20from%20in-house%20pharmacies%2C%20particularly%20when%20the%20same%20drug%20or%20product%20is%20available%20cheaper%20elsewhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20central%20government%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20was%20told%20to%20frame%20guidelines%20to%20guard%20against%20private%20hospitals%20and%20medical%20institutions%20exploiting%20citizens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%2C%20though%2C%20also%20noted%20it%20may%20not%20be%20advisable%20for%20it%20to%20issue%20mandatory%20directions%2C%20but%20that%20it%20is%20necessary%20to%20sensitise%20state%20governments%20on%20this%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20had%20earlier%20issued%20notice%20to%20states%20on%20this%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECounter-affidavits%20had%20been%20filed%20by%20several%20states%2C%20including%20Orissa%2C%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Bihar%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20Rajasthan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20issue%20of%20medicine%20prices%2C%20states%20said%20they%20relied%20on%20price%20control%20orders%20issued%20by%20the%20centre%2C%20and%20that%20prices%20of%20essential%20drugs%20are%20fixed%20to%20ensure%20availability%20at%20reasonable%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20their%20response%2C%20they%20also%20questioned%20the%20locus%20standi%2C%20or%20right%20to%20be%20heard%20on%20behalf%20of%20an%20individual%20or%20group%2C%20of%20the%20petitioners%2C%20pointing%20out%20that%20fair-price%20shops%20have%20been%20set%20up%20for%20government-run%20hospitals.%20On%20this%2C%20the%20court%20noted%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20may%20hasten%20to%20that%20most%20states%20have%20highlighted%20state-run%20schemes%20which%20are%20meant%20to%20ensure%20drugs%2C%20medical%20consumables%2C%20and%20medical%20services%20are%20available%20at%20affordable%20prices.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20centre%20also%20filed%20a%20reply%2C%20in%20which%20it%20said%20there%20is%20no%20compulsion%20for%20patients%20to%20buy%20medicines%20from%20hospital%20pharmacies.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741074240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2018-09%2F17h39ta8_pharmacy-generic-reuters_625x300_13_September_18.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-news-we-agree-supreme-court-on-regulating-drug-prices-by-private-hospitals-7844281%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22State%20governments%20have%20failed%20in%20ensuring%20affordable%20medical%20care%20and%20infrastructure%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20Tuesday%2C%20offering%20scathing%20criticism%20of%20states'%20failure%20to%20deliver%20reasonably-priced%20medicines%2C%20particularly%20in%20case%20of%20essential%20drugs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-news-we-agree-supreme-court-on-regulating-drug-prices-by-private-hospitals-7844281%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kubbra%20on%20the%20emotional%20turmoil%20of%20going%20through%20abortion%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741074081000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-118703121%2Cimgsize-37964.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fkubbra-sait-recalls-going-through-an-abortion-all-alone-without-telling-anyone-i-felt-week-wondered-what-if-i-died%2Farticleshow%2F118703140.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiat