20Ministry%20of%20Defence%20prior%20to%20publication.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%2C%20Dr%20S%20Jaishankar%20had%20briefed%20parliament%20on%20December%204%2C%20on%20the%20situation%20along%20the%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''China%20is%20in%20illegal%20occupation%20of%2038%2C000%20Sq.%20kms.%20of%20Indian%20territory%20in%20Aksai%20Chin%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%201962%20conflict%20and%20the%20events%20that%20preceded%20it.%20Furthermore%2C%20Pakistan%20illegally%20ceded%205180%20Sq.%20kms.%20of%20Indian%20territory%20to%20China%2C%20which%20has%20been%20under%20its%20occupation%20since%201948.%20India%20and%20China%20have%20held%20talks%20for%20multiple%20decades%20to%20resolve%20the%20boundary%20issue.%20While%20there%20is%20a%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%20(LAC)%2C%20it%20does%20not%20have%20a%20common%20understanding%20in%20some%20areas.%20We%20remain%20committed%20to%20engaging%20with%20China%20through%20bilateral%20discussions%20to%20arrive%20at%20a%20fair%2C%20reasonable%20and%20mutually%20acceptable%20framework%20for%20boundary%20settlement.''%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741073640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fo23rtec8_maxar_625x300_04_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexclusive-new-chinese-settlements-near-lac-has-roads-power-transformers-7844066%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20new%20Chinese%20settlement%2C%20with%20at%20least%2091%20independent%20weather-proof%20structures%2C%20is%20near%20completion%20on%20the%20South%20Bank%20of%20the%20Pangong%20Lake%20in%20Ladakh.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexclusive-new-chinese-settlements-near-lac-has-roads-power-transformers-7844066%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20warns%20firms%20on%20H-1B%20visa%20bias%3A%20No%20favouritism%20for%20mi