nd%20I%20truly%20enjoy%20it.%20My%20job%20involves%20guiding%20tourists%20into%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20forest%2C%20and%20I%20share%20details%20of%20the%20forest%20and%20wildlife%20with%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ganeshi%20Kalme%20(32)%2C%20who%20has%20been%20working%20at%20the%20reserve%20as%20a%20guide%20since%202021%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20not%20afraid%20to%20venture%20deep%20into%20the%20jungle.%20I%20find%20it%20thrilling%20to%20encounter%20diverse%20wildlife%20like%20tigers%2C%20sambar%2C%20and%20chital.%20Surprisingly%2C%20when%20I%20saw%20a%20tiger%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20I%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20scared.%20I%20feel%20strong%20and%20empowered%2C%20and%20tourists%20are%20pleased%20to%20see%20a%20female%20guide%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Conservation%20is%20not%20a%20one-day%20job%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKrishnamoorthy%20also%20launched%20the%20Satpura%20Workers%20Society%20to%20involve%20staff%20and%20patrol%20watchers%20in%20managing%20ecotourism%2C%20benefiting%20their%20welfare.%20The%20650-member%20society%20manages%20business%20worth%20about%20Rs%202.5%20crore%2C%20channelling%20profits%20back%20to%20staff%20welfare.%20%E2%80%9CSo%20again%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20game%20changer%20in%20the%20management%20that%20every%20individual%20who%20is%20working%20in%20the%20tiger%20reserve%20is%20reaping%20the%20benefits%20of%20tourism%2C%20and%20they%20connect%20with%20the%20park%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20mentions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20much%20work%20remains%2C%20Krishnamoorthy%20and%20his%20dedicated%20team%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20have%20not%20gone%20unnoticed.%20Satpura%20Tiger%20Reserve%20has%20received%20numerous%20accolades%2C%20including%20the%20prestigious%20WWF%20Wildlife%20Conservation%20Award%20and%20the%202022%20TX2%20Award.%20The%20reserve%20was%20ranked%20as%20the%20second-best%20tiger%20reserve%20by%20the%20