e%20US%20Office%20of%20Personnel%20Management%20(OPM)%20has%20been%20asked%20to%20allocate%20millions%20of%20dollars%20to%20fund%20positions%20in%20billionaire%20Elon%20Musk's%20Department%20of%20Government%20Efficiency%20(DOGE).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20request%20covers%20costs%20for%2020%20full-time%20roles%20from%20January%2020%20to%20July%204%2C%202026%2C%20with%20the%20total%20amount%20potentially%20exceeding%20%244%20million%2C%20according%20to%20a%20draft%20agreement%20obtained%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2025%2F03%2F03%2Fpolitics%2Fdoge-wants-to-charge-opm-millions%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECNN%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agreement%20requires%20OPM%20to%20make%20advance%20monthly%20payments%20for%20DOGE's%20work.%20It%20also%20includes%20a%20clause%20saying%20that%20if%20DOGE%20does%20less%20work%20than%20expected%2C%20it%20may%20reimburse%20the%20agency.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agreement%20specifies%20that%20the%2020%20positions%20at%20DOGE%20would%20be%20paid%20at%20the%20highest%20of%2015%20federal%20pay%20grades%2C%20with%20salaries%20starting%20at%20%24141%2C817%20annually%20and%20reaching%20%24189%2C950%20in%20the%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20area.%20Over%20the%2017.5-month%20period%2C%20this%20would%20total%20approximately%20%244.1%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20remains%20unclear%20whether%20any%20payments%20have%20already%20been%20made.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20draft%2C%20DOGE%20will%20help%20modernise%20OPM's%20IT%20systems%2C%20citing%20an%20%26quot%3Bimmediate%20and%20critical%20need%26quot%3B%20for%20upgrades%20that%20the%20agency%20is%20not%20equipped%20to%20handle%20alone.%20OPM%20would%20also%20be%20required%20to%20grant%20DOGE%20access%20to%20its%20data%20and%20systems%20while%20providing%20operational%20and%20technical%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20OPM%20employee%2C%20against%20the%20arrangement%2C%20told%20CNN%2C%20%26quot%3BSome%20people%20think%20they%20are%20working%20for%20free.%20No%2C%20we%20are%20paying.%20It's%20like%20having%20a%20contract%20with%20an%20entity%20to%20perform%20services%2C%20except%20this%20is%20forced%20on%20us%2C%20so%20we%20are%20forced%20to%20do%20an%20agreement%20to%20retain%20their%20services.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELittle%20information%20has%20been%20disclosed%20about%20DOGE's%20budget%20and%20funding%20sources.%20The%20department%20operates%20under%20the%20Office%20of%20Management%20and%20Budget%2C%20which%20shields%20it%20from%20federal%20public%20records%20laws.%20The%20White%20House%20has%20said%20that%20Musk%20is%20not%20the%20administrator%20of%20DOGE%20but%20serves%20as%20an%20adviser%20to%20President%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20a%20role%20protected%20under%20executive%20privilege.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuestions%20remain%20about%20how%20much%20of%20DOGE's%20initiatives%20are%20costing%20taxpayers.%20Musk%20has%20described%20himself%20as%20a%20volunteer%2C%20while%20DOGE%20employees%20have%20undefined%20roles.%20%26quot%3BSome%20people%20are%20federal%20employees%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fremarks%2F2025%2F02%2Finterview-of-president-trump-and-elon-musk-by-sean-hannity-the-sean-hannity-show%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20Fox%20News%20host%20Sean%20Hannity.%20%26quot%3BBut%20it's%20fair%20to%20say%20that%20the%20software%20engineers%20at%20DOGE%20could%20be%20earning%20millions%20of%20dollars%20a%20year%20and%20instead%20are%20earning%20a%20small%20fraction%20of%20that%20as%20federal%20employees.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusk%20has%20been%20vocal%20about%20his%20views%20on%20government%20spending.%20Earlier%2C%20in%20a%20podcast%20with%20Joe%20Rogan%2C%20he%20called%20government-funded%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musk-doge-us-funded-ngos-may-be-biggest-scam-ever-elon-musks-big-charge-7830007%5C%22%3ENGOs%20%26quot%3Ba%20nightmare%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20suggested%20they%20were%20a%20loophole%20for%20financial%20gain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDOGE%20has%20framed%20its%20work%20as%20a%20necessary%20step%20to%20reduce%20wasteful%20spending%2C%20arguing%20that%20the%20US%20government%20is%20losing%20%242%20trillion%20a%20year%20and%20failing%20audits.%20Elon%20Musk%20cited%20an%20example%20where%20a%20%2412%20billion%20allocation%20to%20the%20Navy%20resulted%20in%20no%20extra%20submarines.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741070340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fjpl37a38_elon-musk_625x300_04_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musks-doge-seeks-millions-from-this-federal-agency-for-efficiency-work-7843649%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Donald%20Trump%20has%20put%20Elon%20Musk%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20DOGE%2C%20tasking%20him%20with%20slashing%20public%20spending%20and%20tackling%20alleged%20waste%20and%20corruption.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musks-doge-seeks-millions-from-this-federal-agency-for-efficiency-work-7843649%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Indians%20are%20bad%E2%80%99%3A%20Florida%20man%20breaks%20Indian%20nurse%E2%80%99s%20face%2C%20hurls%20racist%20slurs%20after%20assault%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741070234000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-118701477%2Cimgsize-644403.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Findians-are-bad-florida-man-accused-of-breaking-essentially-every-bone-in-indian-origin-nurses-face-made-racist-remarks-after-assault%2Farticleshow%2F118701021.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiat