potential%20she%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20recognised.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20explained%20my%20natural%20ability%20to%20equalise%20(adjusting%20the%20air%20pressure%20in%20the%20middle%20ear%20to%20the%20water%20pressure%20)%20as%20a%20key%20advantage.%20I%20initially%20hesitated%2C%20wanting%20to%20refine%20my%20skills%2C%20and%20then%20dedicated%20myself%20to%20training%20in%20Indonesia%20and%20the%20Philippines%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShubham%E2%80%99s%20influence%20has%20been%20profound.%20%E2%80%9CHis%20generous%20sharing%20of%20knowledge%2C%20his%20secure%20support%20in%20this%20field%2C%20and%20his%20emphasis%20on%20ocean%20conservation%20over%20competition%20have%20shaped%20my%20approach%20to%20diving%20and%20mentorship%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Archana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98I%20want%20to%20make%20freediving%20accessible%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArchana%E2%80%99s%20vision%20extends%20beyond%20personal%20success.%20She%20is%20actively%20working%20to%20bring%20AIDA%20(International%20Association%20for%20the%20Development%20of%20Apnea)%2C%20the%20international%20freediving%20organisation%2C%20to%20India%2C%20making%20the%20sport%20more%20accessible%20to%20aspiring%20divers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20date%2C%20we%20have%20to%20register%20under%20other%20countries%20to%20compete%20in%20an%20international%20diving%20competition.%20If%20India%20gets%20its%20own%20AIDA%2C%20then%20it%20would%20make%20this%20easier%20and%20more%20people%20would%20come%20forward%20to%20compete%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20goal%20is%20to%20master%20the%20techniques%20and%20bring%20this%20knowledge%20back%20to%20India.%C2%A0%20I%20want%20to%20make%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F330663%2Fmajor-vivek-jacob-started-claw-global-training-programmes-for-disabled-persons-in-adventure-sports%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efreediving%20