.com%2F383947%2Fla-nina-effect-explained-climate-impact-india-winter%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eweakening%20La%20Ni%C3%B1a%20phase%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20equatorial%20Pacific%20Ocean%2C%20coupled%20with%20neutral%20Indian%20Ocean%20Dipole%20(IOD)%20conditions%20%E2%80%94%20a%20climate%20pattern%20that%20affects%20sea%20surface%20temperatures%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20%E2%80%94%20is%20setting%20the%20stage%20for%20a%20month%20of%20above-normal%20heat%2C%20as%20per%20meteorologists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20first%20week%2C%20minimum%20nighttime%20temperatures%20will%20be%202-3%20degrees%20above%20normal%20(16-18%20degrees%20Celsius)%20in%20Indore%2C%20Ujjain%2C%20and%20other%20nearby%20areas%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Ved%20Prakash%20Singh%2C%20director%20of%20IMD%20Bhopal%2C%20was%20quoted%20by%20The%20Times%20of%20India%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWarm%20easterly%20winds%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeteorologists%20also%20attribute%20the%20early%20heatwave%20to%20warm%20easterly%20winds.%20Mahesh%20Palawat%2C%20a%20meteorologist%20at%20Skymet%20Weather%2C%20told%20Livemint%20that%20an%20anti-cyclone%20over%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20has%20been%20driving%20warm%20easterly%20winds%20toward%20the%20west%20coast.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20disruption%20in%20the%20usual%20wind%20patterns%20has%20caused%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F343039%2Fgardening-tips-for-summer-watering-tips-how-to-protect-plants-from-heat%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etemperatures%20to%20rise%3C%2Fa%3E%20more%20than%20usual.%20Additionally%2C%20high%20humidity%20levels%20near%20the%20coast%20have%